{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-chapter-level-1-chapter-level-1-tsx","path":"/topics/diverticular-disease/supporting-evidence/","result":{"pageContext":{"chapter":{"id":"8b942243-eed9-557a-9678-01f6c77e2b91","slug":"supporting-evidence","fullItemName":"Supporting evidence","depth":1,"htmlHeader":"<!-- begin field 59a33472-75ba-48d1-a5a1-9d5fe905f318 --><h1>Supporting evidence</h1><!-- end field 59a33472-75ba-48d1-a5a1-9d5fe905f318 -->","summary":null,"htmlStringContent":"<!-- begin item 8515c148-28e1-435b-893b-849a0d5c4683 --><!-- begin field a404a37d-8cca-4230-80fd-a7ad0164fa72 --><p>This CKS topic is largely based on consensus opinion in the World Society of Emergency Surgery (WSES) <em>Guidelines for the management of acute left sided colonic diverticulitis in the emergency setting</em> [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/diverticular-disease/references/\">Sartelli, 2016</a>], expert opinion in the American Gastroenterological Association (AGA) Institute <em>Technical review on the management of acute diverticulitis</em> [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/diverticular-disease/references/\">Strate, 2015</a>], the American Society of Colon and Rectal Surgeons <em>Practice parameters for the treatment of sigmoid diverticulitis</em> [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/diverticular-disease/references/\">Feingold, 2014</a>], the consensus statements <em>International, expert-based, consensus statement regarding the management of acute diverticulitis</em> [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/diverticular-disease/references/\">O&#39;Leary, 2015</a>] and <em>Management of patients with diverticulosis and diverticular disease</em> [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/diverticular-disease/references/\">Tursi, 2016</a>], and expert opinion in the Association of Coloproctology of Great Britain and Ireland (ACPGBI) <em>Commissioning guide: colonic diverticular disease</em> [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/diverticular-disease/references/\">ACPGBI, 2014</a>]. In addition, it is based on a Cochrane systematic review <em>Antibiotics for uncomplicated diverticulitis</em> [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/diverticular-disease/references/\">Shabanzadeh and Wille-Jørgensen, 2012</a>] and expert opinion in several review articles on diverticular disease and diverticulitis. The rationale for the individual recommendations is discussed in the relevant basis for recommendation sections.</p><!-- end field a404a37d-8cca-4230-80fd-a7ad0164fa72 --><!-- end item 8515c148-28e1-435b-893b-849a0d5c4683 -->","topic":{"id":"94c44346-c791-5b97-9e45-bacb8fe90589","topicId":"eee234d5-c667-4944-95d2-a45f5e032286","topicName":"Diverticular disease","slug":"diverticular-disease","lastRevised":"Last revised in January 2021","chapters":[{"id":"5bcd7ed5-7ab4-57a1-a517-99ee8bb7b2d5","fullItemName":"Summary","slug":"summary","subChapters":[]},{"id":"5abc06b8-fef4-5d67-81ce-ee1c71284864","fullItemName":"Have I got the right topic?","slug":"have-i-got-the-right-topic","subChapters":[]},{"id":"71ba91f6-898b-5f69-bd52-93f3b1892ad6","fullItemName":"How up-to-date is this topic?","slug":"how-up-to-date-is-this-topic","subChapters":[{"id":"7460514b-3977-52be-9e12-06486604b194","slug":"changes","fullItemName":"Changes"},{"id":"909831b0-6f3c-5e85-8263-a5e1785b8a49","slug":"update","fullItemName":"Update"}]},{"id":"fcd203c7-5d1a-5fcc-ab90-5286ab76bd2d","fullItemName":"Goals and outcome measures","slug":"goals-outcome-measures","subChapters":[{"id":"2cbe6fe5-f942-566e-9136-915145ba8517","slug":"goals","fullItemName":"Goals"},{"id":"ffcabc25-6966-526d-8382-a5fcf56185ab","slug":"outcome-measures","fullItemName":"Outcome measures"},{"id":"dc0b24e2-e0db-5829-baf5-a7aae6d5ab67","slug":"audit-criteria","fullItemName":"Audit c